  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute",
    "Add the diced tomatoes and cook until they start to break down",
    "Add the chicken breast and cook until browned on all sides and cooked through",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the fish sauce, coconut vinegar, black pepper, and salt",
    "Pour the sauce over the chicken and tomatoes",
    "Simmer the mixture for 10 minutes",
    "Toast the paleo bread and serve with the adobo",
    "Garnish with additional garlic and tomato if desired"
  ],
